00:37:32.590 --> 00:37:34.850
They gave $10 or
they gave $1,000.

00:37:34.850 --> 00:37:36.380
It varies, whatever.

00:37:36.380 --> 00:37:39.280
But those are all really
amazing people who stepped up.

00:37:39.280 --> 00:37:41.819
And it is incredibly humbling
to put something out there

00:37:41.819 --> 00:37:44.110
and to realize that people
are willing to just give you

00:37:44.110 --> 00:37:45.160
their money to do that.

00:37:45.160 --> 00:37:45.885
That is crazy.

00:37:49.371 --> 00:37:50.870
I didn't come out
here with, like, I

00:37:50.870 --> 00:37:51.869
didn't write some paper.

00:37:51.869 --> 00:37:52.880
I'm not a PhD in this.

00:37:52.880 --> 00:37:56.322
I just think it's important.

00:37:56.322 --> 00:37:58.280
And I tried to say
something about it because I

00:37:58.280 --> 00:38:01.735
felt like I needed to.

00:38:01.735 --> 00:38:04.350
And it's very humbling to
get that kind of support

00:38:04.350 --> 00:38:07.720
from this community.

00:38:07.720 --> 00:38:12.040
And as of recently,
we now have--

00:38:13.821 --> 00:38:16.070
well actually there's a
