And he spoke a lot
about this kind of stuff

00:39:52.560 --> 00:39:53.970
in the Ruby community.

00:39:53.970 --> 00:39:55.740
And he had a site
called Devpressed.com.

00:39:55.740 --> 00:39:57.360
And it was down for
a couple of months

00:39:57.360 --> 00:40:00.960
because, like a lot
of things, he was busy

00:40:00.960 --> 00:40:03.930
and something broke and
