So otherwise it's the same.

00:40:09.290 --> 00:40:10.770
It is a place for
people who work

00:40:10.770 --> 00:40:12.780
in tech who are tech
professionals to talk

00:40:12.780 --> 00:40:14.020
about their problems openly.

00:40:14.020 --> 00:40:16.051
They can post-- they
make up an account name.

00:40:16.051 --> 00:40:16.800
It doesn't matter.

00:40:16.800 --> 00:40:18.570
We don't check and
validate that stuff.

00:40:18.570 --> 00:40:20.220
They can post anonymously
about their problems

00:40:20.220 --> 00:40:21.636
and talk with other
people in tech

00:40:21.636 --> 00:40:24.480
about what's going on with
them, their specific issues.

00:40:24.480 --> 00:40:27.717
And that's a forum we
took over this year.

00:40:27.717 --> 00:40:29.800
And I should say I don't
even have a slide for it.

